 hockey venues in the United States]]\n[[Category:Gymnastics venues in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:John and Donald Parkinson buildings]]\n[[Category:Landmarks in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Legends Football League venues]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Aztecs sports facilities|c]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Chargers stadiums]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Dodgers stadiums]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Dons]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Express (USFL) stadiums]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Raiders stadiums]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Rams stadiums]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Wolves sports facilities|c]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Xtreme]]\n[[Category:Mixed martial arts venues in California]]\n[[Category:World War I memorials in the United States]]\n[[Category:Monuments and memorials in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Motorsport venues in California]]\n[[Category:National Football League venues in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:National Historic Landmarks in California]]\n[[Category:National Register of Historic Places in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:North American Soccer League (1968\u20131984) stadiums]]\n[[Category:Professional wrestling venues in California]]\n[[Category:Rugby union stadiums in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:San Diego Toros sports facilities|c]]\n[[Category:Soccer venues in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Sports venues completed in 1923]]\n[[Category:Sports venues in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:Sports venues on the National Register of Historic Places in California]]\n[[Category:United States Football League venues]]\n[[Category:USC Trojans football venues]]\n[[Category:UCLA Bruins football venues]]\n[[Category:Wrestling venues in Los Angeles]]\n[[Category:XFL (2001) venues]]\n[[Category:Venues of the 1932 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Venues of the 1984 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Venues of the 2028 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Olympic stadiums]]\n[[Category:Olympic athletics venues]]\n[[Category:Olympic equestrian venues]]\n[[Category:Olympic field hockey venues]]\n[[Category:Olympic gymnastics venues]]\n